<%# home page %>
<div id="showcase">
	<div class="container-fluid">
		<div class="text-center">
			<div id="hook">
				<h1>Do not wait - Improve your business management today with ziada</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="">
				<%= link_to "Create free account", new_account_url, class: 'btn btn-info btn-lg' %>
				<a href="#about" class="btn btn-default btn-lg">Learn more</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<%# About Section %>
<div id="about" class="jumbotron">
	<div class="container">
		<h1 align="center">What is ziada</h1><br>
		<p class="text-center">Ziada is an online software built for Small and Medium Enterprises to improve daily business processes.</p>
		<p class="text-center">Tasks like selling and sales management, inventory tracking, purchase management, user and employee management and accounting are made much easier with ziada. </p>
		<p class="text-center">Reports generated by the ziada development team assist you in making decisions for growing your business</p>
		<p class="text-center">We believe that running a business should be INTERESTING and still remain as AFFORDABLE as possible.</p>
		<p class="text-center"><a href="#features" class="btn btn-info btn-lg">Check out features</a></p>
	</div>
</div>

<%# Features Section %>
<div id="features">
	<div class="container">
		<h1 align="center">Features of ziada</h1><br>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
				<i class="fa fa-cubes"></i>
				<h5 class="feature-header">Product management</h5>
				<p>Manage product inventory easily and seamlessly from any device. Arrange your products according to various categories for speedy access.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
				<i class="fa fa-credit-card"></i>
				<h5 class="feature-header">Create and view sales from anywhere</h5>
				<p>Create sales and purchase stock products in your business with real time inventory update after transactions.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
				<i class="fa fa-users"></i>
				<h5 class="feature-header">Multi User Software</h5>
				<p>Ziada is a multi user software. Create user accounts in your ziada account to have other people help you with carrying out transactions</p>
			</div>
		</div> <br><!-- .row-->
		
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
				<i class="fa fa-line-chart"></i>
				<h5 class="feature-header">Reports and Analytics</h5>
				<p>Ziada provides basic reports. Advanced reports are also generated on request by the ziada management team</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
